00:16:25.410 --> 00:16:26.745
[LAUGHING]

00:16:26.745 --> 00:16:28.120
ARALYN BEAUMONT:
Not the "verde?"

00:16:28.120 --> 00:16:32.650
CHRIS YING: But I also like the
"verde" for different purposes,

00:16:32.650 --> 00:16:34.530
like green eggs and ham.

00:16:34.530 --> 00:16:35.830
ARALYN BEAUMONT: Oh, yeah.

00:16:35.830 --> 00:16:41.930
And at our favorite place north
of the city, at El Molino,

00:16:41.930 --> 00:16:44.195
Karen Taylor uses
green chorizo a lot.

00:16:44.195 --> 00:16:45.070
CHRIS YING: Oh, yeah.

