Let's just not even
do the rest of it.

00:21:03.780 --> 00:21:04.040
BRANDON CHALK: Perfect.

00:21:04.040 --> 00:21:06.248
CHRIS YING: Why don't you
mix these together by hand?

00:21:06.248 --> 00:21:07.850
[LAUGHTER]

00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:10.790
BRANDON CHALK: Thank you, Chris.

00:21:10.790 --> 00:21:14.724
CHRIS YING: I love so much
that you volunteered for this.

00:21:14.724 --> 00:21:15.640
ARALYN BEAUMONT: Here.

00:21:18.676 --> 00:21:19.300
CHRIS YING: OK.

