Meanwhile, let me get
the-- you stay here.

00:21:24.660 --> 00:21:26.524
Do we have the other pork?

00:21:26.524 --> 00:21:27.024
OK.

00:21:30.010 --> 00:21:31.337
Are you not done yet?

00:21:31.337 --> 00:21:32.545
BRANDON CHALK: Uh, it's done.

00:21:32.545 --> 00:21:33.461
CHRIS YING: All right.

