So this is it.

00:21:34.100 --> 00:21:35.900
I mean, the rest of
the pork would kind of

00:21:35.900 --> 00:21:41.161
make the proportions right,
but this is-- where am I going?

00:21:41.161 --> 00:21:41.660
Here.

00:21:41.660 --> 00:21:44.130
[LAUGHTER]

00:21:44.130 --> 00:21:44.630
This is it.

00:21:44.630 --> 00:21:45.296
This is chorizo.

