You can buy quality
meat and be sort of

00:21:56.680 --> 00:22:00.110
certain of the provenance
of where you got this.

00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:01.295
It's not from a shady place.

00:22:03.960 --> 00:22:06.180
That's chorizo.

00:22:06.180 --> 00:22:09.100
This is red chorizo.

