CHRIS YING: All right.

00:22:27.951 --> 00:22:29.850
Like, that's it.

00:22:29.850 --> 00:22:32.270
Stick it on there.

00:22:32.270 --> 00:22:35.430
You wait until it's burnt,
until it's blackened.

